{"tid":1426712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[不合作運動] 遍地開case，投訴黑警","createTime":"2019-08-07T03:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T15:43:59.000Z","uid":265234,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ac638322ea7a6bb6de9e6b4f08baa73257b0072d","tid":1426712,"uid":265234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:31:45.000Z","msg":"作為和理非的一員，眼見連日來前線勇武打游擊衝擊警署，我地可以諗下另一條戰線對抗黑警，就係同佢玩制度，打<span style=\"color: red;\">消耗戰</span>。<br />\n<br />\n服務行業既人都知，香港人一向出名擅長投訴，無論理由幾勉強都可以據理力爭，能言善辯，我地一於發揮所長，去各區警署報案作<span style=\"color: red;\">正式投訴</span>。<br />\n<br />\n投訴目的唔係需要黑警接納投訴，目標係要佢地<span style=\"color: red;\">花時間跟進處理</span>，雖然大家都知黑警成日唔依程序做野，但文書野有記錄有服務承諾佢地反而會睇得緊，黑警內部都好鍾意睇門面野同睇數字，佢地會攞d嘉許信打飛機同寫apprasial，所以投訴未必無用，而且呢個方法抗爭<span style=\"color: red;\">成本同風險都好低</span>。<br />\n<br />\n睇返2014-2018數字，每年投訴警察數字都係得二千到三千幾宗，就算2014咁大件事都係得四千多d。呢度求其一個熱門post既正評都唔止呢個數啦。<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到既係，要投訴既內容唔係612，721元朗果類世界性單一大case，而係各種唔同既個別事件，內容以親身經歷最好，又唔一定要同夢境有關，既然黑警咁好想像力話雷射筆係武器，大家點解唔可以一齊動腦筋發揮下想像力?<br />\n<br />\n然後，一定有人會問，無狗牌編號點投訴?<br />\n監警會網頁咁寫:<br />\n<em>//在下述情況下，指控會被列為「無法追查」︰<br />\n- 不能確定被投訴的警務人員的身份<br />\n<br />\n上述定義不表示若果投訴人未能確定被投訴人的身份，投訴警察課便不會採取進一步行動。投訴警察課會根據所得資料，盡量追查被投訴人的身份；只有追查不果時，才會作出未能確定被投訴人身份的結論//</em><br />\n<br />\n有編號有主角當然最好啦，但無既就盡量提供確實地點，時間，職級，服裝等資料，佢查唔到都可以追問佢攞下資料同記錄，目標係要打消耗戰。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有無巴絲有投訴黑警經驗可以分享下? <br />\n<br />\n參考資料:<br />\n投訴警察有關資料<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/11_useful_info/cap.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F11_useful_info%2Fcap.html&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apC3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=da7ff039\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/11_useful_info/cap.html</a><br />\n<br />\n警察通例 第 26 章-投訴警察個案及內部調查<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pgo/tc/Cpgo026.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fdoc%2Fpgo%2Ftc%2FCpgo026.pdf&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apC3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=9c0ec101\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/pgo/tc/Cpgo026.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n監警會資料<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ipcc.gov.hk/tc/complaints/procedure_chart.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipcc.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcomplaints%2Fprocedure_chart.html&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apC3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=129709a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ipcc.gov.hk/tc/complaints/procedure_chart.html</a>"},{"pid":"1a608263f930bb86b0645bf42592f36559ca4a21","tid":1426712,"uid":265234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:38:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cffd1b4ba781b471c73293774ad1a3ea02a1b300","tid":1426712,"uid":148960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:39:04.000Z","msg":"互推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[綜合討論] 目前運動出現嘅問題以至未來方向<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dydHsS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dydHsS</a>"},{"pid":"d20b6f4b7cf38aff76981ee488144886babeed6a","tid":1426712,"uid":265234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:20:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ed769ebf7ca0251feec6bb00a81892f58b255a8","tid":1426712,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:24:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df593a46c760cc803174de2fe42f982d2cc2808d","tid":1426712,"uid":62247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:30:02.000Z","msg":"自己人查自己人算鳩數啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0d5d1dd30ca934e762e6500b09496c12ed8f54e","tid":1426712,"uid":265234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df593a46c760cc803174de2fe42f982d2cc2808d","tid":1426712,"uid":62247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:30:02.000Z","msg":"自己人查自己人算鳩數啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:47:24.000Z","msg":"都係各自出一分力打下消耗戰，目標係要佢交d野出黎，再睇下有無位追擊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429ec29c517540d5b2636aa7b12b0f03995f3ae6","tid":1426712,"uid":265234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:48:39.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n有無得做，都歡迎討論下，俾下意見"},{"pid":"0c9fbaed8f5ef3026bc53eac2156ad53bfbe9f31","tid":1426712,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:51:05.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"a0f15d2ce80fce0767a0c8a3f0a62c7a313552cc","tid":1426712,"uid":285413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:08:08.000Z","msg":"如果我哋相信法治，如果我哋想未來香港有法治<br />\n一定要做<br />\n<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484f8f0073e4bf0fa3b0340d90f3ef33ab9478f1","tid":1426712,"uid":265234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:11:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"239c3f45bfdcd1b83d9c971702b2662da52ad9fa","tid":1426712,"uid":265234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:49:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bfc4aafbb83e3ddcca86e1763fd8be2e25d55cbc","tid":1426712,"uid":265234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:56:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97c22a79b7c9659807a0dbe57372cafcee532b82","tid":1426712,"uid":265234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:33:36.000Z","msg":"投訴題材:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/efuEu7m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FefuEu7m.jpg&h=f9fe45fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1aefbffe56bd325f3327dd12170a0db54ad4cfd","tid":1426712,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:38:37.000Z","msg":"上次聽過曾健超講，直接報案，會比投訴更有用。"},{"pid":"8e1cbcfc8304d42be0cc1c125ffc8cef820747cb","tid":1426712,"uid":265234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d1aefbffe56bd325f3327dd12170a0db54ad4cfd","tid":1426712,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:38:37.000Z","msg":"上次聽過曾健超講，直接報案，會比投訴更有用。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:00:04.000Z","msg":"如果有黑警犯事既證據，當然係報案啦，但無證據就真係唔可以亂報。<br />\n<br />\n但投訴門檻相對較低，可以係兇人，不禮貌，不合警察通例既行為，目標係大家都可以做，唔需要係成功投訴獲接納。"},{"pid":"a572153e0eac796232f285348be9da8f68d99457","tid":1426712,"uid":265234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:43:59.000Z","msg":"push"}]}